THIRD-PARTY ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This project builds on the following open-source frameworks and datasets:

  - TRL (Transformer Reinforcement Learning) — Apache 2.0
    https://github.com/huggingface/trl

  - PEFT (Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning) — Apache 2.0
    https://github.com/huggingface/peft

  - Unsloth — Apache 2.0
    https://github.com/unslothai/unsloth

  - sentence-transformers — Apache 2.0
    https://github.com/UKPLab/sentence-transformers

  - τ²-Bench (tau-bench) — MIT
    https://github.com/sierra-research/tau-bench

The benchmark design is informed by the following academic works (full
citations in REFERENCES.md):
  Gebru et al. (2021), Pushkarna et al. (2022), Meng et al. (2024),
  Zhou et al. (2023), Rafailov et al. (2023), Gu et al. (2024),
  Liu et al. (2024), Chen et al. (2025), Li et al. (2025),
  Park et al. (2024), Bai et al. (2022).
